Live Streaming Shopee Liga 1 2019 di Vidio: Bhayangkara FC Vs Semen Padang
02 Nov 2019, 16:30 by Bola.net
Bola.net - Bhayangkara FC tidak tampil mengesankan sepanjang pagelaran Shopee Liga 12019. Mereka berkutat di papan tengah dan kesulitan untuk menembus papan atas.
Untuk menghindari keterpurukan lebih lanjut, Bhayangkara FC harus meneruskan tren positif di tiga pertandingan terakhir. Dalam tiga laga, Bhayangkara FC berhasil menang dua dan sekali imbang.
Misi menang juga sepertinya akan diusung Bhayangkara FC saat menjamu Semen Padang di stadion PTIK, Sabtu (2/11/2019). Apalagi Semen Padang sedang menghuni posisi paling bawah.
Klub asal Minang ini menelan tiga kekalahan di tiga laga terakhir. Sulit bagi skuat Eduardo Almeida ini untuk bangkit apalagi main di kandang lawan.
Live streaming Bhayangkara FC melawan Semen Padang FC bisa mulai Anda saksikan pada pukul 18.30. Dapatkan link live streaming Bhayangkara FC vs Semen Padang di halaman berikutnya...
text:
Live Streaming Shopee Liga 1 2019 in Vidio: Bhayangkara FC vs Semen Padang
02 Nov 2019, 16:30 by Bola.net
Bola.net - Bhayangkara FC did not impress during the Shopee Liga 12019 performance. They struggled in the middle of the board and had difficulty penetrating the top flight.
To avoid further deterioration, Bhayangkara FC must continue the positive trend in the last three matches. In three matches, Bhayangkara FC have won two and drawn one.
The winning mission is also likely to be carried by Bhayangkara FC when entertaining Semen Padang at the PTIK stadium on Saturday (11/2/2019). Moreover, Semen Padang is currently occupying the lowest position.
The Minang club has lost three of its last three matches. It is difficult for Eduardo Almeida's squad to get up, let alone play at home to the opponent.
You can watch Bhayangkara FC live against Semen Padang FC at 18:30. Get the live streaming link of Bhayangkara FC vs Semen Padang on the next page ...
